{"tid":1910762,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英次子陷二手檸茶奉客醜聞    出事餐廳「四季常餐」突執笠","createTime":"2020-03-05T01:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T09:20:09.000Z","uid":79563,"like":76,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"6a3981bdda2d743d951830bbe550c26e47a7ca8f","tid":1910762,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:51:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/AiSatoMOQavpsgmdbl1Ncg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/88684a4d1d1f6df0e8ddd46fd946385f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FAiSatoMOQavpsgmdbl1Ncg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F88684a4d1d1f6df0e8ddd46fd946385f&h=735001e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由壹傳媒黎智英次子黎耀恩在中環所開的茶餐廳「四季常餐」，早前爆出「二手凍檸茶」奉客醜聞後，食物環境衞生署接獲4宗投訴並對負責人作出衞生教育，但連日來仍遭網民大鬧，不是斥責在新冠肺炎肆虐下，醜行如同「播毒」，便是留言冷嘲熱諷。事件發酵多日後，出事的茶餐廳今日(4日)突然在門外貼上結束營業的告示。東網記者到現場所見，餐廳今日未有營業，門外貼上「本店於2020年3月4日結束營業」，着顧客到中環另一分店。<br />\n<br />\n四季常餐的「二手凍檸茶」醜聞之所以被篤爆，全因有光顧涉事茶餐廳的網民，點了一杯「少甜」的凍檸檬茶後，反而獲送上偏甜的凍檸檬茶，在客人投訴後，職員便取走該凍檸檬茶並放入雪櫃，但隨後被發現該「二手凍檸茶」拿給其他客人飲用。<br />\n<br />\n四季常餐的醜事被曝光後，雖然在Facebook專頁認錯歉道歉，，但網民依然憤憤難平，在其專頁留言追擊，大罵「聽見都嘔心」，有人更諷刺可推出名為「二手飯」的食品，甚至改為名「二手常餐」。<br />\n<br />\n食環署早前回覆東網指，近日共接獲4宗與查詢事宜相關的投訴，該署派員到該食肆調查，其衞生情況尚可。該署人員已向負責人給予衞生教育，提醒他們須時刻注意食物安全，以及個人和環境衞生。該署人員會對持牌食肆進行定期巡查，確保食物業經營者時刻遵守相關法例，以及發牌及持牌條件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/pocQC9fSw1gUuWDCkE6DZg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/onccinstantnews.com/825445cdad3948ab07a4f447bddc623b\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpocQC9fSw1gUuWDCkE6DZg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fonccinstantnews.com%2F825445cdad3948ab07a4f447bddc623b&h=8a947122&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e91961452d4d330290bcdf9de4ec89e1633b977b","tid":1910762,"uid":254813,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"加上方向報個app成日有呢單新聞追擊！"},{"pid":"ecf317138f1a6825fc0d400e24872a32dcc5b8cb","tid":1910762,"uid":222614,"like":4,"dislike":21,"score":-17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:59:09.000Z","msg":"黃店？"},{"pid":"4c36618dd6fae570830cf12139ccfe1db4f7d2bb","tid":1910762,"uid":79563,"like":203,"dislike":6,"score":197,"quote":{"pid":"ecf317138f1a6825fc0d400e24872a32dcc5b8cb","tid":1910762,"uid":222614,"like":4,"dislike":21,"score":-17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T01:59:09.000Z","msg":"黃店？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:01:28.000Z","msg":"印象中係藍<br />\n<br />\n老豆同仔係兩個獨立個體嚟, 無關係的"},{"pid":"45a498e75b81e53853eddf4f45686b763681d238","tid":1910762,"uid":33370,"like":165,"dislike":6,"score":159,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"藍店咪藍店囉<br />\n蕭生同佢個仔都一黃一藍啦<br />\n唔通個個連登仔咁好彩　父母一樣都係黃咩"},{"pid":"84c6d97d51446825ba5bea6ab9dda58adb170000","tid":1910762,"uid":79563,"like":86,"dislike":5,"score":81,"quote":{"pid":"45a498e75b81e53853eddf4f45686b763681d238","tid":1910762,"uid":33370,"like":165,"dislike":6,"score":159,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:03:45.000Z","msg":"藍店咪藍店囉<br />\n蕭生同佢個仔都一黃一藍啦<br />\n唔通個個連登仔咁好彩　父母一樣都係黃咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:05:00.000Z","msg":"華夏思想, 係好鍾意將父母同子女連結  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b700a65800e0b2f8a12710e47ff4f190e2a735","tid":1910762,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:05:03.000Z","msg":"衰過印度"},{"pid":"c397de486dc0ca449a8a6d78a7bfde3ef2ddfac6","tid":1910762,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:05:09.000Z","msg":"衞生教育即係咩"},{"pid":"d85ee88d236dc45ec7d8625487af2508f389d581","tid":1910762,"uid":239651,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T02:17:00.000Z","msg":"諗